devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b11be94f4b417000ab570c04f640e383c376db4","tid":1045931,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbf1834c47346530bc02b535da294a1298f13f8","tid":1045931,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf9a1003cd6d3c71cfda954990f811ea1a78a76","tid":1045931,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"375d717d5d8db5e2c3060c8d2f750765c77ac0bd","tid":1045931,"uid":128261,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"感覺上啲憎泛民多過建制既毓粉（例如仇思達）有湯家驊化既傾向<br />\n開始講野甚有「中間派」既feel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T18:50:46.000Z","msg":"任亮憲都走中間派，黃毓民及其毓粉或者都得<br />\n佢地同整個反對派為敵，走向中間同建制都無可厚非<br />\n可以講韓國瑜果套，香港發大財，反正黃毓民撐韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b63c4b123692381cb3570e686edfc0770ed0dbe","tid":1045931,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ecba22fec951caad25baaf8d3119af3565a979","tid":1045931,"uid":75139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b22aa214c6f686905f9f8ec8bdde96dfe9a6c0","tid":1045931,"uid":36134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T01:16:12.000Z","msg":"如果神駒係讀埋大<br />\n佢應該會係第一個因政治因素被踢出校"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"神駒9up 就叻，邊有關sir 咁勇武<br />\n點會比人開除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1f026f209923e61961aeb14dbb8e1d02df89bc"